lead_paragraph: Milwaukee Brewers right-hander Zach Davies had his no-hit bid ended by a two-run homer from Oakland's Billy Butler with two outs in the seventh inning.

headline.print_headline: Brewers RHP Zach Davies Loses No-Hit Bid in 7th Inning
